      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BREAKOUT LAD (1) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 30.09 beating WHITE MACK. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. LITTLE CLIFFY (2) flew the lids off the inside draw with a fast early split and gave a sight, finishing a 3.5 lengths second (30.13) over 520m at this track. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Well-placed to take this out. TAHITIAN GIRL (8) is a progressive type who recorded her 15th career win last time out (29.88) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. One of the prime contenders. ALIIR (3) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - in the mix again.",
